snippet.title: Sonic Before the Sequel Aftermath - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
This is a fan game where you have to collect itens in order to progress trough the world. that's it, but there is some decisions i made i'm sure fanboys will get pissed off about.

oh, btw, the music in this video is Technology Tree Zone from After the Sequel Made by Funk Fiction.
